headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid ABT and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Abbott Laboratories’s 16.6% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 12.8%, and its stock price has climbed to $136.50 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
